        Current running state of the directory domain in synchronization life cycle. It could be one of the following five states. SELECTIVE_FULL_SYNC and SELECTIVE_DELTA_SYNC are sync states for selective sync. This property may be present in responses from the server, but if it is present in a request to server it will be ignored.
